S{R[Am-c] and R[Mag-m] (right nostril stopped); R[Calc] (inclination to breathe deeply); R[Kali-bi] (tough mucus); R[Aur] and R[Puls] (laughter alternately with weeping); R[Sars], R[Lyc], R[Benz-ac] (strong urine, crying before urination; but these three have gravel: with R[Bor] it is from inflammation of mucous membrane); R[Arum-t] (sore mouth); R[Graph] (trichiasis); R[Bell] (hot leucorrhoea); R[Sep] (small ulcers about joints); R[Bar-c] (cobweb-sensation); R[Nat-s] (cheerful after stool).}

